-- Collins Stewart Hires Sharma, Dunstan From ICAP for Stock Derivatives Desk
-- B y   A l e x i s   X y d i a s
-- 2010-11-11T15:42:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-11/collins-stewart-hires-sharma-dunstan-from-icap-for-stock-derivatives-desk.html
Collins Stewart Plc  has hired  Roger Sharma  and  Brad Dunstan  from ICAP Plc to start an equity-
derivatives trading desk, the London-based brokerage said.  Sharma and Dunstan joined this week as co-heads of European
Equity Derivatives and will report to  Jonathan Geering , head of
trading, according to an e-mailed statement today. Sharma and
Dunstan worked for Bear Stearns Cos. before joining ICAP,
according to the release.  To contact the reporter on this story:
